'
<p>Well, the end of the summer has not only approached the majority of us, it\'s passed us by. Suddenly, I\'m starting to see a lot of away messages that read: <i>\'HW. I hate my teachers. Help,\'</i> or <i>\'working,\'</i> or <i>\'procrastinating.\'</i> Last year\'s seniors went to college, this year\'s got their senior photos, and <i>bam!</i>, we\'re heaving our heavy backpacks and heading towards that dreaded torture chamber.</p>
